+-------------------------------
  pattern matching rule
------------------------------+
driver pm:
load $pro_lib.console.(*);

** pattern matching expression
rule pm(p1,p2 ∈ N) ∈ N =>
  (0 if p1 = 0 
  ,1 if p2 = 0  
  ,2 if p1 = p2 
  ,3 if p1 > p2
  ,4 if True );
** execute pm expression
print pm(0,2); // 0
print pm(1,0); // 1
print pm(1,1); // 2
print pm(1,2); // 3
print pm(2,1); // 4

over.

